<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>vīraśrī narasiṁhyadēvaṁkara vijayarājyasaṁvatsa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>raṁbulu 1324 Agunneṁṭi puṣya śukla paurnnamī ca
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁdravārānanu kāśyapagōtrulaina viṣṇudāsaŪpādhyā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yala manumaṁḍu prayāgaUpādhyāyala koḍuku ka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷiṁgavyāpāri laḍḍesurathāṇu tammuṁḍu reṣidāsanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yuṁḍu tamaku ĀyurārōgyaAiśvaryābhivṛddhigānu
<lb n="7"/>putrapautrābhivṛddhiyuṁgānu śrīkūrmmanāthuni sannidhini Ā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkasthāyiṁgānu Akhaṁḍadīpamunaku <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dīrgāsi pōlabō
<lb n="9" break="no"/>yaṁḍu paḷlabōyaṁḍu vīri gōcarānanu peṭṭina goṟya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lu 100 Iṁdulaku neyi nitya Aḍyaṁṭi lekkanu Ēṁḍādi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kini nālgu puṭlu paṁduṁ lekkanu śrīkūrmmarāyani nagara
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nu pravēśamu cēyaṁgalāru I dhammamu tirupāti
<lb n="13"/>śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa<note n="429-1">At the bottom of this inscription numeral 4 above it.</note><supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

